- "weight of their sacks" refers to the total number of sacks made;
- "strength of their tackles" refers to the total number of tackles made;
- "sharpness of their interceptions" refers to the total number of interceptions made.

sql:
SELECT game_id, sacks, tackles
FROM games
ORDER BY sacks DESC, tackles DESC;

external_knowledge:
- "Total performance" is calculated as the sum of sacks, tackles, and interceptions for each player;
- "Average performance ratings" are calculated as the mean of the performance ratings for each player;
- "Injury details" include the total number of injuries and the total recovery days.
